Third Department,

May, 1947.

(May 5, 1947.) In the Matter of the Claim of Edward Iskenderian, Respondent, against Western Photo Engraving Co., Inc., et al., Appellants. Workmen’s Compensation Board, Respondent.

Decision of this court, handed down March 12, 1947 (271 App. Div. 1041), modified to read as follows: Award affirmed, with costs to the Workmen’s Compensation Board and the claimant, to be divided equally between them, and with disbursements to each against the appellants. All concur.
